#Google

#To restrict websites to a specific Domain; on the google search bar type <site:xyz.com>. i.e oscp.com

    site:oscp.com

#To filter out a specific subdomain, in this case web do -site:www.oscp.com
#why? try to find an ftp for example

    site:oscp.com -site:www.oscp.com

#Furthermore, to look for a specific filetype use <filetype:ext>. i.e pdf

    site:oscp.com -site:www.oscp.com filetype:pdf 

#On search settings, access Advanced search for extended filters (if unsure about syntax)
#Search for Google Syntax (must)




